OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FLord Peter Mandelson apparently
OL,7,F"declined to comply" with a request to
OL,8,Fhand over his personal phone and allow
OL,9,Fthe government to publish WhatsApp
OL,10,Fmessages and other information related
OL,11,Fto his appointment, documents
OL,12,Fpublished alongside thousands of
OL,13,Fdocuments about the posting have
OL,14,Frevealed.
OL,16,FThe Cabinet Office put forward a
OL,17,Frequest on March 31 2026, to
OL,18,FMandelson, via his solicitors, to
OL,19,Frequest any information held on his
OL,20,Fpersonal phone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
