OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FAs Mandelson declined, the government
OL,7,Fhad "no further recourse" to search
OL,8,Fhis device.
OL,10,FThe second tranche of documents
OL,11,Frelating to Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Fdecision to give the prestigious
OL,13,FWashington job to Lord Mandelson
OL,14,Frather than a career diplomat was
OL,15,Freleased by the government on Monday
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FThe files show that in a handwritten
OL,7,Fnote, Mandelson told the then Foreign
OL,8,FSecretary, David Lammy, that the
OL,9,Fgovernment would "never regret" his
OL,10,Fappointment as US ambassador.
OL,12,FHe went on to say that it would be a
OL,13,F"huge honour" to serve as ambassador
OL,14,Fto the US.
OL,16,FWhat do the files show?
OL,18,FConcerns previously raised about
OL,19,FMandelson's security clearance being
OL,20,Frushed through are strengthened in
OL,21,Fthese files.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
