PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FA Foreign Office official told the
OL,7,FSecret Intelligence Service (SIS) that
OL,8,FMandelson "is yet to receive his DV
OL,9,Fclearance", but due to the timeframe
OL,10,Fof his appointment and his role as a
OL,11,FPrivy Counsellor, seniors gave
OL,12,FMandelson access to more classified
OL,13,Fmaterial.
OL,15,FThe vetting originally showed that
OL,16,FStarmer's appointment of Mandelson was
OL,17,Fa "reputational risk", particularly
OL,18,Frelating to his links with Russia and
OL,19,FChina.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
