OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FWhatsApp messages between Mandelson
OL,7,Fand Work and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,8,FMcFadden reveal heavy criticism of the
OL,9,Fprime minister's leadership.
OL,11,FMandelson told McFadden that the PM
OL,12,F"is not leading from the front" and
OL,13,Fgoes on to say that he believes things
OL,14,Fin Number 10 are "not good" and after
OL,15,Fa visit to Number 10 himself,
OL,16,FMandelson claims it "is beleaguered
OL,17,Fand bereft".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
