FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FTalking of unrest within the party,
OL,7,FMcFadden says Labour MPs are always
OL,8,Fasking "who can we tax in order to pay
OL,9,Fbenefits to others" while also
OL,10,Fbranding the welfare reforms as "very
OL,11,Fbad".
OL,13,FIn February, MPs voted to demand
OL,14,Fministers publish a range of documents
OL,15,Frelating to the appointment, using an
OL,16,Farchaic parliamentary process called a
OL,17,F"humble address" following the launch
OL,18,Fof a police investigation into Lord
OL,19,FMandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
