PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780398175
OL,3,CMandelson 'declined to comply' with
OL,4,Crequest to hand over WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FThe first batch of files was released
OL,7,Fin March and included due diligence
OL,8,Fand advice provided to the prime
OL,9,Fminister, warning him of the
OL,10,F"reputational risks" of appointing
OL,11,FMandelson to the role.
OL,13,FMandelson was sacked in September 2025
OL,14,Ffollowing further revelations about
OL,15,Fhis relationship with convicted
OL,16,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein, for which
OL,17,Fhe had previously apologised, claiming
OL,18,Fhe did not witness wrongdoing in his
OL,19,Finteractions with Epstein and "deeply
OL,20,Fregrets" continuing his relationship
OL,21,Ffor so long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
